reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute meets Functional & Affordable
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. These brushes are so soft! It's like a soft cloud decided to take up makeup artistry! Seriously, they could maybe even rival the softest bunny!Practicality: They come in a soft storage bag for travel. Additionally, I store the sponges and little face scrubbies in the clear cubby provided.Aesthetically: This is such a pretty shade of pink. And the little sponges are in a very pleasing pallet of pinks that simply makes my heart happy to look at!I haven’t had them long enough to need to clean them (they were a gift at Christmas), but thus far I haven’t noticed any bristle loss! In summary, this is a great value on what seem to be good quality brushes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars it is what it is.
reviews.reviewText: i ordered two sets of make up brushes. one was pink the other was supposed to be purple. has nothing to do with the brushes or how they are used, great product. The pink set has pink bristles and pink handles almost a barbie pink. The purple set has softer almost baby pink handles and purple bristles. I am aware that colors of actual product often do not match the image used. What i ordered and what i wanted were purple bristles with purple handles. what i got was purple bristles with pink handles. yes i get that the color of the handles have no effect on the brushes and their intended use. the point of this review is i was expecting something in a specific color, what i got does not even come close to being in the same color family as purple.
